      <template #text>
        <p>The Persona 3 experience becomes even more enjoyable while retaining its originality.</p>
        <p>A more exhilarating battle system and new graphics and gimmicks make Tartarus easier to explore. Dormitory life and community have also legitimately evolved!</p>
